= Rashish Tandon (राशीश टंडन)

~~~
{}{img_left}{IMG_2818.jpg}{me}{265px}{280px}{}
I am a ML Engineer at Apple, based in Seattle.

Prior to joining Apple, I was a graduate student (PhD) in the [http://www.cs.utexas.edu/ Department of Computer Science] at [http://www.utexas.edu/ UT Austin], advised by [http://users.ece.utexas.edu/~dimakis/ Alex Dimakis] and [http://www.cs.utexas.edu/~pradeepr/ Pradeep Ravikumar](now at CMU). My PhD thesis dealt with machine learning in high-dimensional and distributed settings. Prior to joining UT Austin, I obtained a B.Tech/M.Tech(Dual Degree) in CS from [http://www.iitk.ac.in/ IIT Kanpur] in 2011.

~~~

